DTSTAMP:20260321T224056Z
DTSTART:20260327T170000Z
DESCRIPTION:Taught by Amanda Long of Amanda Metals. Join us for an engaging
	 and creative experience in this copper plant stick workshop! You will be 
	creating three different copper and crystal glass bead plant sticks that w
	ill transform your greenery into stunning displays. Whether you’re a begin
	ner or an experienced creator\, this workshop is designed to inspire your 
